                        <div class="col-lg-12">
                            <p class="text-justify">STRUTT is building the largest collection of Travel bags & Travel Gear for the Modern Traveller.</p>
                            <p class="text-justify">Our Collection of Travel bags is already big and we continue to add more & more  products which aim to make your Travel easy & convenient.</p>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                Now you can rest and leave us to worry about your packing list.</p>
                            <strong class="text-justify">
                               Our Current Collection includes
                            </strong>
                            <ul>
                                   <li>Travel Bags – Cabin Bags ll Duffle Bags ll Hitchhikers ll Limited edition bags</li>
                                   <li>Backpacks – Travel Backpacks ll Buddy Packs </li>
                                   <li>Business Travellers – Suit Duffels ll Modular overnighters</li>
                                   <li>Leisure Travel – Weekenders ll Magpie Trippers</li>
                                   <li>One Day travel – Everyday bag ll Wingman collection</li>
                                    <li>Travel Essentials – Packing Cubes ll Toiletry kits ll Travel Soaps ll Essential Oils</li>
                                    <li>Travel Accessories – Bumbags ll Passport Wallets ll Travel Wallets ll Slings</li>
                               </ul>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                We are continuously working on growing the travel collection, bringing you products which will make your travel easy and fun. 
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                <strong>Cabin Bags :: </strong>
                                These are Travel bags which are designed for easy in cabin carry. These Travel bags are compact yet spacious, light-weight which make them easy to carry, Convenient to use and access, Easy to store and Super Stylish to match your travel personality. These are designed as your inflight baggage and easily fit in the overhead compartments. They can carry 3 to 4 T shirts 2 pairs of jeans toiletries, a pair of shoes with a little space for more. These bags can be the ideal travel companion for 2- 3 days depending on if you are a lightweight or a heavy weight packer.
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                <strong>Duffle Bags :: </strong>
                                These Travel bags are slightly bigger than the Cabin bag. They are ideal to carry for 3- 4 day trip with multi pockets. The Purpose of these bags is to be a companion to your suitcase. All of them come with a trolley strap. These are Stylish, Spacious, Colorful, Lightweight and collapsible travel bags which are easy to store. These travel bags can carry 4 – 5 Shirts, 2 pairs of jeans/lowers, a pair of shoes. These bags can be the ideal travel companion for 2- 3 days depending on if you are a lightweight or a heavy weight packer.
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                <strong>Hitchhikers :: </strong>
                                Are a smarter version the Barracks bag. They are vertical duffle bags. Ideal for bikers or trekkers and they are usually carried as a crossbody bag that can carry clothes for 1- 2 days. They pack vertically like a rucksack.  Small and compact. Extremely lightweight and very easy to store. These bags can carry 2 to 3 T shirts 1 pairs of jeans toiletries, a pair of shoes with a little space for more. These bags can be the ideal travel companion for 1-2  days .
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                <strong>Travel backpacks :: </strong>
                                These backpacks are ideally designed very smartly to carry both your clothes and Laptops. The bags are designed with 2 different sections – one for your laptop & 1 for your clothes & toiletries. In design they are compact ,lightweight and can be used for daily office use when you are not travelling.  They can carry clothes for upto 3 days. Most of these travelling backpacks come with inbuilt packing strips. 1 Section you can carry your laptop, charger and other electronic items and the other section is for your clothes and toiletries.  Their master designs eliminate the need of any other bag for short trips. 
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                <strong>Buddy packs :: </strong>
                                These Backpacks were designed for everything extra. These are small, compact, lightweight and designed for the day to day outings on your trip. They have space for everything that is essential and everything else that doesn’t fit in your suitcase. They can fit under the seat on an Airplane. Ideal for Cameras, Important documents, essential electronics wallets etc. They have hidden pockets. Now you don’t have to struggle with excess baggage with any airline, whatever doesn’t fit in your suitcase you can put in  Buddy and carry it on your flight. 
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                <strong>Business Travellers :: </strong>
                                Business Men & Women, Corporate Men and Women, The bag to carry your Suits, sarees and official wear  on your work trips  wrinkle free is finally here. There is a separate sleeve for your suits and a separate section for the rest of your belongings. In some designs you can  Carry the sleeve separately which basically allows you to just carry the duffel bag when you are not on a work trip. These bags are large in size and can carry clothes and gear for upto 4 days. Lightweight, Spacious and Ergonomically designed. 
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                <strong>Modular Overnighters ::  </strong>
                                These are one of a kind bags made for solo travellers who frequently take short trips. The bags are designed as smart bags. They come in 2 different sections. One for clothes and one for your laptop. The clothes section packs like a soft suitcase and the laptop side is designed like a standard laptop bag.  The beauty of this bag is that when you travel you carry it as one single bag and when you reach your hotel room , you detach the clothes section completely and leave it in the room while you go carry just the laptop bag for work. Then when you are about to leave you reattach the bag and carry it back as a single bag. The clothes section can pack clothes for 1-2 days and comes with inbuilt packing straps
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                <strong>Weekenders :: </strong>
                                Are the colorful bright large weekend duffle bags. The have different inbuilt sections and compartments to carry everything you want. They are ideal for a 4- 5 day trip and have space for your electronics, clothes, travel games, that extra pair of shoes and so much more. They are large enough to carry for your weekend trips or if you driving across states on a long trip. 
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                <strong>Magpie Trippers :: </strong>
                                These bags have specially been designed for women and girls. They are bright and colorful. They have been made in a drum shape with long twin handles. The Purpose of the long Twin handles is so that you can carry the bag like a backpack when you don’t feel like holding them on your hand or shoulders. They are ideal for overnight trips or your gym. They can carry a change of clothes, toiletries and shoes. Extremely light weight for ease of carrying and collapsible for easy storage.
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                <strong>Everyday bags :: </strong>
                                We understand travel starts the minute you step out of the house. We are here to provide a solution for everything you want to and need to carry for every trip you make. These Everyday bags are here to solve that purpose. These are small bags which can carry your knickknacks in and make a trip to nearby day locations. 
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                <strong>Wingman Series :: </strong>
                                These bags are also for Day travel however they all come with either inbuilt or separate packing cubes. These sections help you navigate and segregate your packing. They are small bags with segregated space which enables you to pack smarter. 
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                <strong>Packing Cubes :: </strong>
                                Have become an essential part of the packing story. They are basically small bags which are sized and designed to fit different elements of your packing list. They generally come in sets of 4 till 10. There will be a separate one for your Shirts, pants, undergarments, nightsuits, toiletries, makeup, Shoes, Socks , Electronics and sometimes laundry too. They come in different shapes and sizes but generally each set is designed to comfortably fit in your Suitcases or Carry ons. It makes packing easier, it makes access to stuff while on your trip easier and it helps you to pack more since it organizes your packing list. 
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                <strong>Toiletry Kits :: </strong>
                                These kits are specifically designed for your toiletries like Toothbrush, travel shampoos , soaps, creams etc. They however can also double for a Make up pouch, A jewelry pouch , A shaving kit  or just as a storage bag for your small knickknacks. Its always better to travel with one of these so that you can be sure your toothbrush is not rubbing with your shoes or laundry. They come in all shapes and colors and its generally better to pick the one which is more spacious but is compact in design.
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                <strong>Travel Soaps :: </strong>
                                Finding a good soap on trips is more difficult than you can imagine and now more than ever we understand the importance of frequently washing our Hands. Today smart skin care brands have come up with the most ideal solution for this. They are making Pocket soaps which are easy to carry, easy to store are organic and smell great. They have 2 versions – 1 Use and throw and the second are small pocket sized travel reusable soaps for your Toiletry kits. It also doubles as a great product for daily use.
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                <strong>Essential Oils :: </strong>
                                Sometimes Travel causes discomfort, insomnia, anxiety or you just take some time acclimatizing your self to a new location. This is where Essential oils come in handy. Now they are available in Pocket roll on sizes. You can put them in your jeans pocket, the slip in pocket of your bag or just add them to your toiletry kit. They come for different purposes and are now available in travel sizes. 
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                <strong>Bumbags :: </strong>
                                Have somewhat become an essential part of every trip. Its time to understand why. When you are travelling and you leave all your luggage behind in your hotel room and step out  you definitely don’t want to be carry another heavy bag to carry most basic of essentials. This is where bumbags save our lives. They fit on the waist in your belt – are perfectly sized for your keys, cash, passport, mints, phone, wallet and little more of the small things. They are light weight, convenient and you don’t have to worry about leaving them behind in the café you sat down to try something new to eat.
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                <strong>Passport Wallets :: </strong>
                                The Passport is this little booklet which generally gets lost in your bag and like any other notebook withers away if not looked after. The smartest way to save it for 10 years is to give it a Cover. That’s what passport wallets are. They come in all shapes and sizes and all colors. Some even solve the problem of taking care of your boarding pass so that you don’t loose it in the waiting area. Most of them now come with card & cash slots so they double up as a wallet so you don’t have to carry 2.
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                <strong>Travel Wallets :: </strong>
                                These are different from passport wallets. When you are travelling you are definitely not going to carry every currency note you own and every not so important card or paper which is currently taking up space in your present wallet. Travel should be light , convenient & easy, you should be able to carry everything that is important in the most convenient way. Travel wallets solve that purpose. They are compact, convenient to use, extremely light weight and only have space for what is important for you to carry. Our collection is one of a kind and we can assure you once you start using a Batua you will never want to use another wallet again
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                <strong>Slings :: </strong>
                                Another Small sized shoulder bag which makes travel easy. Not everybody wears a belt and for those we have the travel sling. They are spacious enough for everything important like your keys, wallet, docs, mints etc and extremely light weight on the shoulder to carry.
                                <br /><br />
                            </p>
